The names here were all over the place and there were missing versions. Harmonise the names and add the missing versions.


---

Deletions:

- ...

Any other comments you want to keep out of the PR commit should go
below the `---`, and placed outside this HTML comment, or else they

If this PR depends on other PRs, please list them below this comment,
using the following format:
- [ ] depends on: #abc [optional extra text]
- [ ] depends on: #xyz [optional extra text]

Before I fix downstream uses, I would like to know whether people think my names are good or not. I see two minor issues with them:
* ~~What I am naming `fooEquiv` is the `Equiv` such that `fooEquiv.invFun = foo`, not `fooEquiv.toFun = foo`.~~ Fixed by turning the equivs around
* The rest of the library contains things like `MeasurableEquiv.finFoo` rather than `Fin.fooMeasurableEquiv`.
